name: Google Cloud Cloud SQL SqlServer with outdated engine versions
query: { cloudSqlInstances (where: { engine: "sqlserver" OR: [ {engineVersion_STARTS_WITH: "2012"}, {engineVersion_STARTS_WITH: "2008"}, {engineVersion_STARTS_WITH: "2005"}, {engineVersion_STARTS_WITH: "2000"} ] }) { identifier accountID cloudAccountID cloudAccountName cloudProvider idFromProvider internalAssetType internalName internalRegion assetCategory } }
